{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a boolean value indicating whether this array is identical to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"other"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Swift"}],"externalID":"s:Sa20isTriviallyIdentical2toSbSayxG_tF","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isTriviallyIdentical","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"to","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": `Self`","kind":"text"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"extendedModule":"Swift","title":"isTriviallyIdentical(to:)","symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Array"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["/documentation/swift/array/istriviallyidentical(to:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Array/isTriviallyIdentical(to:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isTriviallyIdentical"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"to"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":": `Self`"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Two array values are identical if there is no way to distinguish between"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"them."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For any values "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"a"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"b"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"c"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(to: a)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is always "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". (Reflexivity)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(to: b)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implies "},{"code":"b.isTriviallyIdentical(to: a)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(Symmetry)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(to: b)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"b.isTriviallyIdentical(to: c)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are both "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then "},{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(to: c)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is also "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(Transitivity)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"a","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"b","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" are "},{"code":"Equatable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then "},{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(b)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"a == b","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". "},{"code":"a == b","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" does not imply "},{"code":"a.isTriviallyIdentical(b)","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Values produced by copying the same value, with no intervening mutations,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"compare as identical:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let d = c","print(c.isTriviallyIdentical(to: d))","// Prints true."],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Comparing arrays this way"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"includes comparing implementation details that are normally hidden,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the memory location of any underlying array storage,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These details aren’t considered when comparing for equality with the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"=="},{"type":"text","text":" operator."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Therefore, identical arrays are guaranteed to compare equal,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but not all equal arrays are identical."}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"O(1)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Complexity","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Bool":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Bool","type":"topic","title":"Bool","kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/bool","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Bool"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Bool"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A value type whose instances are either ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Array/isTriviallyIdentical(to:)":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Array/isTriviallyIdentical(to:)","t